---
title: Green Thai Prawn Stir Fry With Bok Choy & Jasmine Rice
description: Nourishing, flavour-packed, and bursting with fresh green veggies, this nourishing 25-minute curry is a guaranteed crowd-pleaser. Our special Thai curry paste gives the dish a brilliant kick of heat, whilst the peanut garnish adds a beautiful layer of texture. Served on a bed of steamed rice, and topped with chopped coriander this is fast food at its best.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/green-thai-prawn-stir-fry-b69ae2c7-c9e5619f.jpg
